sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Consumer
  participant S as configService
  participant P as Providers
  participant D as Domain (precedence+schema)
  participant K as Cache
  participant E as EventPublisher port
  participant W as Watchers

  Note over C,S: init() / reload()
  C->>S: reload()
  S->>P: load() (each provider, timed)
  P-->>S: { key: value } bags
  S->>D: precedence.resolve(layers)
  D-->>S: { values, origins }
  S->>D: schema.validate(values)
  alt valid
    D-->>S: { ok:true, normalized }
    S->>S: diff(previous, effective)
    S->>K: cache.set(snapshot, version+1)
    S->>W: notify changed keys (old,new,ts,version,origin)
    S->>E: publish ConfigurationChanged (redacted) + ConfigurationReloaded
    S-->>C: { ok:true, version, changed }
  else invalid
    D-->>S: { ok:false, errors }
    S->>E: publish ConfigurationValidationFailed
    S->>E: publish ConfigurationRollback (keep previous)
    S-->>C: { ok:false, rolledBack:true, errors }
  end

  Note over C,S: read path (synchronous)
  C->>S: get(key)
  S->>K: read cached snapshot
  K-->>S: value
  S-->>C: value (raw); snapshot()/logs redacted
